#9604
Antechamber~
You have now entered the chambers of Ishamael Bgreathiou.  The opening
antechamber is expansive, and very elabourate.  Crimson carpeting touches
your feet, and banners proudly displaying the many kingdoms who swore fealty
to him in the past.  Torches barely light this place, and there are a set of
twin stairwell, and a small corridor directly in front of you.  
~
