#9608
An Iron Bound Door~
As you approach the iron bound door, the walls begin to spill off of what
you used to call the wall and ceiling, and roll into your path, creating a
wall of human skin, a golem of flesh to bar your path.  You see an eye or
two pop out of it, to glare at you, and the sickening cries become shouts of
alarm, warning you to back away from the Keep of Ultan Bgreathiou,
Infernalist Sorcerer.  
~
