The Library of Bgreathiou~
You enter a massive library, as far as the eye can see are shelves upon
shelves of books, pertaining to all subjects, many that Ishamael wrote
himself.  The walls extend out in a pattern that seems to ignore the laws of
space and time.  There are a few chairs sitting in corners and nooks in the
library, for those who are visiting to read and educate themselves about the
world surrounding them.  
