A small office~
A small desk sits in this corner, with a small chair to go with it.  A
portrait of what seems to be a gigantic black mountain piercing the heavens
with its tip rests on the wall.  Sitting behind this desk is a creature
wearing all black, who makes no sound as he moves though his voice sounds as
