#9619
A strange gateway~
The once serene background that was the library suddenly fades away to
black, and the chanting returns, a large portal stands before you now.  It
is made of a strange spiked wreath, almost as if it were once human flesh. 
If you peer beyond this and into the portal you see what was in the
painting, almost as if it were the backyard of hell itself.  Black clouds,
large black mountains, cries of pain, the sound of whips, fire and bestial
roars.  
~
