The Chambers of Orion Bgreathiou~
This room is dark, and red flames flicker in the darkness, occasionally
flaring to reveal a sparsely decorated room.  Drawn onto the wood panel
floor is a pentacle, with the blood of an animal one would think.  The
flames dance on each point of the star.  In the midst of these flames sits a
man with a strange reddish tint to his skin, very leathery.  Wings are
draped about his shoulders, and in his hands he holds a broad, black staff,
which he levels at you as you enter.  
~
