#9653
The Quarters of Danyeal Tedronai~
This room is very extravagant, a broad room with a series of candelabra,
the room itself having a very strange presence to it.  The bed is large, and
so is the dresser.  In the corner rests a longsword, heron marked.  Standing
in front of the door as you walk in is Danyeal himself, looking at you with
a distrustful glare.  
~
