#9654
Hallway~
The hallway pans out more, and a pair of larger doors are on either wall,
one leading into the bed chamber of the Master, and the other into his
Brothers hold.  As you saw in the torture chambers, men in black robes
holding in their bare hands the sickly flames of balefire to illuminate your
path are here, guiding you onward.  
~
