#9655
Ultan Bgreathiou's Bedchamber~
This room is made of a strange black stone.  The room itself feels alive,
and as you enter, the door slams shut, and a beast stands in your path, over
twelve feet tall, flames billowing around him.  His bed is small and looks
to be uncomfortable, but he doesn't overly seem to mind.  No light
penetrates this room, only the flames of balefire that surround his
impressive physical form.  
~
