#9658
A Dais~
The stone dais is raised high over the ground, a monument of stone and
shadow.  A large altar rests in the middle, a young woman writhing upon it,
slices methodically placed upon her flesh in a strange pattern.  A powerful
wind howls here, and it seems to scream and bellow unintelligibily.  Moving
past the Dais, you see a room that is covered in a inpenetrable blackness.  
~
