#9660
The Top of the Tower~
You reach the very top of the Tower, standing outside in the cool wind. 
The wind you heard within the Tower seems more potent here, its ramblings
not quite so random now.  The stars glitter in the sky like diamonds, The
horrors that you endured within the tower just a dream.  Then, the gate you
entered at the top shuts, and you find yourself trapped at the top, all you
can hear is that dull horrid shouting, and beyond it a soft, subtle laughter
...  
~
